{"id":908,"parent_id":905,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":908,"title":"Joel 3","subtitle":"","short_title":"Joel","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 3"],[".studySummary",["i","All nations will be at war—Multitudes will stand in the valley of decision as the Second Coming draws near—The Lord will dwell in Zion."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.1","order":"02.30.003.60985"},["b","1"],"For, behold, in those days, and in that time, when I shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"bring again the captivity"],"of Judah and Jerusalem,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.2","order":"02.30.003.60986"},["b","2"],"I will also",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"gather"],"all nations, and will bring them down into the valley of Jehoshaphat, and will",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"plead"],"with them there for my people and",["i","for"],"my",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"heritage"],"Israel, whom they have scattered among the nations, and parted my land."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.3","order":"02.30.003.60987"},["b","3"],"And they have cast lots for my people; and have given a boy for an harlot, and sold a girl for wine, that they might drink."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.4","order":"02.30.003.60988"},["b","4"],"Yea, and what have ye to do with me, O Tyre, and Zidon, and all the coasts of Palestine? will ye render me a recompence? and if ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"recompense"],"me, swiftly",["i","and"],"speedily will I return your",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"recompence"],"upon your own head;"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.5","order":"02.30.003.60989"},["b","5"],"Because ye have taken my silver and my gold, and have carried into your temples my goodly pleasant things:"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.6","order":"02.30.003.60990"},["b","6"],"The children also of Judah and the children of Jerusalem have ye sold unto the Grecians, that ye might remove them far from their border."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.7","order":"02.30.003.60991"},["b","7"],"Behold, I will raise them out of the place whither ye have sold them, and will return your recompence upon your own head:"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.8","order":"02.30.003.60992"},["b","8"],"And I will sell your sons and your daughters into the hand of the children of Judah, and they shall sell them to the Sabeans, to a people far off: for the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath spoken",["i","it."]],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.9","order":"02.30.003.60993"},["b","9"],"¶Proclaim ye this among the Gentiles; Prepare",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"war"],", wake up the mighty men, let all the men of war draw near; let them come up:"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.10","order":"02.30.003.60994"},["b","10"],"Beat your plowshares into swords, and your pruninghooks into spears: let the weak say, I",["i","am"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"strong"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.11","order":"02.30.003.60995"},["b","11"],"Assemble yourselves, and come, all ye heathen, and gather yourselves together round about: thither cause thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"mighty"],"ones to come down, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.12","order":"02.30.003.60996"},["b","12"],"Let the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"heathen"],"be wakened, and come up to the valley of Jehoshaphat: for there will I sit to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"judge"],"all the heathen round about."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.13","order":"02.30.003.60997"},["b","13"],"Put ye in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"sickle"],", for the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"harvest"],"is ripe: come, get you down; for the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"press"],"is full, the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_13d"},"fats"],"overflow; for their wickedness",["i","is"],"great."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.14","order":"02.30.003.60998"},["b","14"],"Multitudes,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"multitudes"],"in the valley of decision: for the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"day"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","is"],"near in the valley of decision."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.15","order":"02.30.003.60999"},["b","15"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"sun"],"and the moon shall be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"darkened"],", and the stars shall withdraw their shining."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.16","order":"02.30.003.61000"},["b","16"],"The",["span.smallCaps",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"Lord"]],"also shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"roar"],"out of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_16c"},"Zion"],", and",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_16d"},"utter"],"his voice from Jerusalem; and the heavens and the earth shall",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_16e"},"shake"],": but the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","will be"],"the",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_16f"},"hope"],"of his people, and the strength of the children of Israel."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.17","order":"02.30.003.61001"},["b","17"],"So shall ye know that I",["i","am"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"dwelling"],"in Zion, my holy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"mountain"],": then shall",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"Jerusalem"],"be holy, and there shall no",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_17d"},"strangers"],"pass through her any more."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.18","order":"02.30.003.61002"},["b","18"],"¶And it shall come to pass in that day,",["i","that"],"the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"mountains"],"shall drop down new wine, and the hills shall flow with milk, and all the rivers of Judah shall flow with waters, and a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"fountain"],"shall come forth of the house of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and shall water the valley of Shittim."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.19","order":"02.30.003.61003"},["b","19"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"Egypt"],"shall be a desolation, and Edom shall be a desolate wilderness, for the violence",["i","against"],"the children of Judah, because they have shed innocent blood in their land."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.20","order":"02.30.003.61004"},["b","20"],"But Judah shall dwell for ever, and Jerusalem from generation to generation."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.21","order":"02.30.003.61005"},["b","21"],"For I will cleanse their blood",["i","that"],"I have not cleansed: for the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"dwelleth in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"Zion"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.1a","order":"02.30.003.61006"},["b","1a"],["span.small","HEB"],"cause the return."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.2a","order":"02.30.003.61008"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.11"},"Micah 4:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.8"},"Zeph. 3:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.2b","order":"02.30.003.61010"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.16"},"Isa. 66:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.31"},"Jer. 25:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/38.22"},"Ezek. 38:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.2c","order":"02.30.003.61012"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.25"},"Isa. 19:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.4a","order":"02.30.003.61014"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reward"},"TG Reward"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.4b","order":"02.30.003.61016"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/32.35"},"Deut. 32:35"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.9a","order":"02.30.003.61018"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/war"},"TG War"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.10a","order":"02.30.003.61020"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.10"},"2 Cor. 12:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/11.34"},"Heb. 11:34"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/12.27"},"Ether 12:27"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/50.16"},"D&C 50:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.11a","order":"02.30.003.61022"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/13.3"},"Isa. 13:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.12a","order":"02.30.003.61024"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/heathen"},"TG Heathen"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.12b","order":"02.30.003.61026"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-judge"},"TG Jesus Christ, Judge"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.13a","order":"02.30.003.61028"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/26.5"},"Alma 26:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/4.4"},"D&C 4:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.13b","order":"02.30.003.61030"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/6.3"},"D&C 6:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.64"},"101:64"],"."],["div",{"id":"13c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.13c","order":"02.30.003.61032"},["b","13c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.19"},"Rev. 14:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.107"},"D&C 76:107"],"."],["div",{"id":"13d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.13d","order":"02.30.003.61034"},["b","13d"],["span.smal